                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;bin/mahout throws NoClassDefFoundError: org/apache/hadoop/util/ProgramDriver&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think this is due to line 224&lt;br/&gt;
    CLASSPATH=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{CLASSPATH}:${MAHOUT_HOME/lib/hadoop/*}&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
I fix the issue by moving the closing brace&lt;br/&gt;
    CLASSPATH=&quot;${CLASSPATH}
&lt;p&gt;:$&lt;/p&gt;
{MAHOUT_HOME}
&lt;p&gt;/lib/hadoop/*&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
